          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2020-06-09T14:35:44Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Respect Graduate Student Workers Act</b><br> <br> This bill prohibits the National Labor Relations Board from promulgating or enforcing any rule that excludes student workers at private universities from the definition of <i>employee</i> under federal labor laws. (Under current law, students paid for services provided at universities in connection with such students' studies are considered employees.)</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-01-21T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
